<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比跑进厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21700</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈……爸爸没有死，对吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21700</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“亲爱的孩子，爸爸当然没有死！你为什么会这么想？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我……我不知道。”鲍比没有说箱子里衣服的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈抱了抱她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“上次联系时，你爸爸还好好儿的呢。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“总有一天，他会回到我们身边的。别乱想了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，妈妈来到女孩儿们的房间，她要和菲利斯一起睡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58277</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得也在那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈。”彼得说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在跟我们讲讲那个俄国人的故事吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们耐心等待了这么久，故事要越长越好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今晚不能讲长故事了。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我太累了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比听出来妈妈哭过了，但是其他孩子们不知道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就尽量长一些吧。”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比依偎在妈妈身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。”妈妈开始讲，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这位先生叫舍潘斯基，他写了一本关于穷人的书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但在俄国，评判富人是违反沙皇规定的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以舍潘斯基先生在西伯利亚的监狱被关了3年。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，这一定不是真的！”彼得大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是真的。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他因为自己的想法被关进了监狱，他并没有犯什么罪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寒冷的冬天里，犯人们要在矿井里工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果有人病了，就只能等死。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是怎么从监狱出来的？”菲利斯问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是逃出来的。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他的妻子和孩子已经离开俄国来到英国。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他不知道他们在哪里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果他能找到家人，他们也许会一起住在这里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈看上去很伤心，说：“让我们一起为那些犯人祈祷吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171213</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>祈祷后，他们就上床睡觉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是鲍比很晚都没有睡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她决定写一封信给老先生，并请求第二天早上跟他见面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>亲爱的老先生：我有一件事非常想问您。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不是向您要东西，妈妈说那样是错的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193900</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我只想跟您讨论关于一位犯人的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>希望您明天能下车和我聊聊天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>您的小朋友：鲍比</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，老先生下车时，鲍比在等他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来。”老先生拍了拍鲍比的肩膀说，“什么事？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，您来了！”鲍比转过身。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……”她把俄国人的事告诉了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！”老先生说，“我看过他的书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的书被翻译成了欧洲各国语言，是非常棒的一本书！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会尽力帮助他的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我就知道您一定会帮助他的！”鲍比兴奋地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251430</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>十天之后，三个孩子坐在山坡上看着5点15分的火车经过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看到老先生下了火车后，就向他跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好消息！”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我找到了俄国作家的家人！你们快点告诉他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280341</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比先跑到家，把这个消息告诉了妈妈和俄国人，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280341</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>俄国人高兴得哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天，他马上坐车赶往伦敦，与妻子和孩子们团聚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>